@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@adminUsername = admin
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456
@existingProjectId = 1
@employeeVisibleProjectId = 1
@invalidProjectId = 0
@missingProjectId = 999999

### 正常路径：管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：管理员获取项目详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{existingProjectId}}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录获取项目详情，预期 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{existingProjectId}}

### 正常路径：普通员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：普通员工获取自己可见的项目详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{employeeVisibleProjectId}}

### 正常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：project_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{invalidProjectId}}

### 异常路径：项目不存在，预期 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{missingProjectId}}
